query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id,
  pwi.productName,
  pwi.locationCode,
  pwi.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pwi.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = 30004
ORDER BY pwi.id;
